snippet.title: Properties of Kites
snippet.description:
I introduce many properties of Kites, work through three examples of finding missing angles, and finish with a quick two column proof.  EXAMPLES 5:55 10:09 12:54 14:46 Find free review test, useful notes and more at http://www.mathplane.com

A HUGE THANK YOU  sent out to kariheedots for Close Captioning this math lesson.  Your help is appreciated very much:) If you'd like to make a donation to support my efforts look for the "Tip the Teacher" button on my channel's homepage www.YouTube.com/Profrobbob
